---
// Franchise band: off-white intro card + photo + animated "Seja um franqueado" card.
// Layout follows Figma: stacked (mobile/tablet), 3-column row on desktop (≥1280).
// Sizes are flat per Figma — heading 36px, paragraph 20px, CTA 48px (60px desktop).
---

<section class="bg-wevol-black py-20 xl:py-24">
  <div class="wv-container grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex min-h-[400px] flex-col justify-center rounded bg-wevol-off-white p-3 xl:h-[500px]">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 px-6 py-2">
        <h2
          class="wv-title flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-4xl leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-wevol-ink xl:justify-start xl:gap-x-5"
          data-reveal="words"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-4 xl:gap-x-5">
            Leve a
            <img src="icons/wevol-logo-dark.svg" alt="WEVOL" class="h-[40px] w-auto" />
          </span>
          <span class="w-full whitespace-nowrap text-center lg:w-auto xl:w-full xl:text-left">
            para sua cidade.
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p
          class="wv-title text-center text-xl leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-wevol-ink xl:text-left"
          data-reveal="lines"
        >
          Conheça a oportunidade de fazer parte da expansão de uma marca que está transformando
          saúde, performance e longevidade.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <img
      src="images/franquia.png"
      alt="Treino com tecnologia WEVOL"
      class="h-[400px] w-full rounded object-cover xl:h-[500px]"
      data-reveal-img
    />

    <a
      href="#"
      class="group relative flex flex-col items-end justify-start gap-20 overflow-hidden rounded bg-gradient-to-l from-wevol-grad-1 to-wevol-grad-2 p-6 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-wevol-orange lg:min-h-0 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-center lg:gap-8 xl:h-[500px] xl:flex-col xl:items-end xl:justify-between"
      data-franquia-cta
    >
      {/* hover: gradient fades into solid WEVOL Orange */}
      <span
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-wevol-orange opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 ease-out group-hover:opacity-100"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></span>

      {/* arrow — 40px (mobile/tablet), 80px (desktop); before the label except on the tablet row */}
      <span
        class="relative order-1 block size-10 shrink-0 overflow-hidden lg:order-2 xl:order-1 xl:size-20"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        {/* arrow exits top-right, twin re-enters from bottom-left */}
        <img
          src="icons/franquia-arrow.svg"
          alt=""
          class="absolute inset-0 size-full transition-transform duration-500 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)] group-hover:translate-x-[110%] group-hover:translate-y-[-110%]"
        />
        <img
          src="icons/franquia-arrow.svg"
          alt=""
          class="absolute inset-0 size-full translate-x-[-110%] translate-y-[110%] transition-transform duration-500 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)] group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:translate-y-0"
        />
      </span>

      <span
        class="wv-title relative order-2 w-full text-right text-5xl leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] text-wevol-ink lg:order-1 lg:w-auto lg:whitespace-nowrap xl:order-2 xl:w-full xl:whitespace-normal xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Seja um franqueado
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
